    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你发现自己被困在这个由自然界的四种元素形成的魔法穹顶内：水、土、空气和火。要逃脱，你必须仔细探索周围环境，解开谜团，解决难题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/cbe2dac3b5a9bc47d5a106f47c1a640b.poster.avif?t=1741742927\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/cbe2dac3b5a9bc47d5a106f47c1a640b.webm?t=1741742927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/cbe2dac3b5a9bc47d5a106f47c1a640b.mp4?t=1741742927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随心所欲地探索，利用自己的时间里，按照自己的顺序，通过找到并抵达各个图腾，一次解除四种元素的魔力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/c5950f76851f93fbc5d2ec4a508c936d.poster.avif?t=1741742927\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/c5950f76851f93fbc5d2ec4a508c936d.webm?t=1741742927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/c5950f76851f93fbc5d2ec4a508c936d.mp4?t=1741742927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在第一人视角中，如果你想逃离这个神秘魔法，你必须使用逻辑，跳出思维定式，并以不同寻常的方式与环境互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特点：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第一人视角；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D 运动；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由、非线性探索；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逻辑谜题；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >环境谜题；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-5 小时的游戏时间；  <br> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D 像素艺术风格图形</p></li></ul>",
